{"tid":631232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豪華巴擬設留座服務","createTime":"2018-04-16T09:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T18:53:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"99ce39f581455ccd21b3c199469bafb9964a077a","tid":631232,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:43:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180416/20362771?_ga=2.74509330.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F20362771%3F_ga%3D2.74509330.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=0955fzHkKFo8gU5cknr%2BFzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=46f78476\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F20362771%3F_ga%3D2.74509330.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=04ae0b80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180416/20362771?_ga=2.74509330.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n豪華巴擬設留座服務<br />\n<br />\n9.8K<br />\n港聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180416/large/18651007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180416%2Flarge%2F18651007.jpg&h=721e3daf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九巴擬於今年內引入新型長途巴士服務（俗稱豪華巴士）。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府早前建議引入新型長途巴士服務（俗稱豪華巴士），九巴擬於今年內，開辦來往屯門及灣仔的P960，及由元朗西往天后的P968配合服務，標榜不設企位較舒適，但車資較類似路線貴五成，被質疑過高。九巴強調，票價難有下調空間，訂造新巴士亦需時，目前時間緊迫，要在今年內推出服務有隱憂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n難於今年推出<br />\n<br />\n目前P960及P968建議票價分別為31.2元及35.1元；兩線同樣較行走類似路線的960及968貴五成。九巴指，因新服務不設企位，中途站亦較少，載客量減少下，定價必然較普通路線貴。九巴曾參考過機場巴士及東鐵綫頭等車票定價，機場巴士A線及E線，東鐵的頭等與普通票，車價差距達一倍，認為新型長途巴士服務，定價已算具競爭力，難有下調空間。新服務亦會引入留座服務，確保乘客有座位。<br />\n<br />\n兩條新線預計要特別訂造12部巴士提供服務，九巴指，目前未有巴士具體設計，要待路線確定能開辦才能落實。惟一般巴士從訂購到製成需時約一年，九巴雖已聯絡生產商預留生產線，但坦承要趕及如期今年內推出服務，時間相當緊迫。九巴又指，新服務未被納入長者2元乘車計劃內，但九巴仍會向長者提供半價，正研究向月票持有人提供折扣。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭啟源<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n紅巴2.0　椅背變薄增空間LCD取代點陣式顯示屏<br />\n<br />\n港聞 12小時前"},{"pid":"e577481d7db12d722b61d07a008607ac93ab265e","tid":631232,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:46:03.000Z","msg":"灣仔去屯門洗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1c7b03fce3b8c3c516c4bd5c8d4c9b71765f59","tid":631232,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:47:51.000Z","msg":"香港人供樓都供到退休<br />\n其實呢d路線有咩人會搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日60蚊來回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49fe7f37019c0260c833e7e6d6ace727274fe3e","tid":631232,"uid":13327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:47:57.000Z","msg":"政府比返村巴做好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2a62878532ff14ebdbd3ed23ba014dc9c2ac91","tid":631232,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b49fe7f37019c0260c833e7e6d6ace727274fe3e","tid":631232,"uid":13327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:47:57.000Z","msg":"政府比返村巴做好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:50:54.000Z","msg":"村巴2+3真係狗座位黎<br />\n<br />\n其實你開係中環交易， 上環港澳開， 上完不設分站就衝上公路就大把人搭"},{"pid":"7fbb01b85c28809e16e96685c0a2d760be94d617","tid":631232,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"夾到個上落車站就話啫<br />\n<br />\n夾唔到又點會快咗。"},{"pid":"69e2351e7b6f8a94d61031374cdef021ba1ff4ee","tid":631232,"uid":38671,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"諗呢d屎